{"tid":1903171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fortune Insight, Business Focus 老細係邊個","createTime":"2020-02-28T19:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T06:45:51.000Z","uid":68779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9a89001dcb311d104023bec3c56e46a431b39b4b","tid":1903171,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"Fortune Insight:收到料 九西總監謝文華醫生 多次脅迫交罷工醫護名單 馬嘉輝醫生請辭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1899940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1899940</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/contact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fcontact&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT2x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=6b09dc6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/contact</a><br />\nD-1B, 7/F, Hoi Bun Industrial Building, 6 Wing Yip Street, Kwun Tong, Kowloon<br />\n另一個好多人like，成40萬既Facebook page又係佢地<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/contact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fcontact&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT2x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=2a7ae88e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/contact</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1576696064449&amp;issue=20191219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1576696064449%26issue%3D20191219&d=OftESTy%2BPOS3A4jdltYT2x6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=772a7072\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1576696064449%26issue%3D20191219&h=4e758a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1576696064449&amp;issue=20191219</a><br />\nFortune Insight入股要求多<br />\n<br />\n有基金朋友說想找財經內容供應商，不知是想做宣傳，還是想直接投資。我說：「現在最大的兩個是<span style=\"color: red;\">Business Focus和Fortune Insight</span>，兩個都有股東是我的朋友，順得哥情失嫂意，我還是兩個都介紹給你認識，你自己決定吧。」<br />\n<br />\n跟着我提了他一句，Fortune Insight的創辦人是個三十出頭的屋邨仔，一心要搞fintech和medical tech，傾過好些媒體投資者，海外又有，本地上市公司又有，因為多多條款要求，所以都say no了。咁有性格，如果你想入股投資，應該不容易了。<br />\n<br />\nBusiness Focus，Fortune Insight 依兩間都好多like，想知佢地背後係咪又係紅色資金好似hk01咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efce404fed98d46ac11ff39cc597c02a4240f3a","tid":1903171,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:48:25.000Z","msg":"Fortune insight 應該算黃？睇咗佢page 好耐，間接引人屌政府多，同埋留言嘅好似全部都屌政府屌警甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amrUhhU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamrUhhU.jpg&h=f4669430&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"305507b36331928a1af4fe3e0128a69942bfbdc2","tid":1903171,"uid":74425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"渾水"},{"pid":"a0eb0cec8cf5af8b9462aa0b759606b08c0e3cdf","tid":1903171,"uid":342527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"305507b36331928a1af4fe3e0128a69942bfbdc2","tid":1903171,"uid":74425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"渾水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:54:39.000Z","msg":"我都估係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a26100af45c56b385b724cd6a0990570bef7175","tid":1903171,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3efce404fed98d46ac11ff39cc597c02a4240f3a","tid":1903171,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:48:25.000Z","msg":"Fortune insight 應該算黃？睇咗佢page 好耐，間接引人屌政府多，同埋留言嘅好似全部都屌政府屌警甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amrUhhU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamrUhhU.jpg&h=f4669430&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:56:18.000Z","msg":"就係唔知先怕，